{"tid":955744,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日股急瀉逾千點美日股市同陷熊市","createTime":"2018-12-25T16:13:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-26T00:29:45.000Z","uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"65e6b10bb62d45dbe5ca12d61522596c4a39a006","tid":955744,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T16:13:52.000Z","msg":"受到美股急挫拖累，亞太區股市普遍下跌，日本股市下瀉超過5%，日經平均指數全日急跌1010點，跌穿2萬點關口，收報19155點，是1年8個月以來最低位，日股由10月份高位回落21%，正式踏入技術性熊市，今次亦是東京股市最大的12月份跌幅 ，亦是10年來最大的單日跌幅。日本財務大臣麻生太郎指，金融市場可能反應過度。<br />\n<br />\n美國股市平安夜市況繼續插水，三大指數都跌超過2%，道瓊斯工業平均指數跌超過600點，納斯達克指數跌140點。標普五百指數跌65點，收報收報2351點，今次是標指歷年平安夜最差表現，並進入技術性熊市，亦意味美股長達十年的牛市告終。"},{"pid":"51838c7253ab41230257d35d3bc3cccf20b98654","tid":955744,"uid":76105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T16:41:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Mo la Mo la <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0ccc649e0cd52769294d7c2da60215c833f1850","tid":955744,"uid":169074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T16:46:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5805aa521d0553acc2bbf990b9ae1cc36dc7cc97","tid":955744,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T00:29:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}